            "marks": [],
            "text": "まとめ"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-80dec3e2-eea0-4fc5-8240-732154e76ef3",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-a65defea-624a-405a-8286-4b328861aa1f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "看護助手の面接でよく聞かれる質問と回答例でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-876fe805-8b63-4357-a1ef-cc73a25c91e0",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-502061da-e7f1-4e49-b287-67502a5e3443",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-c25869c0-48a5-4b40-ab03-16d70c8b4334",
        "_type": "block",
